   MINNEAPOLIS -- Control Data Corp. said it agreed to sell
an 80% interest in VTC Inc., its chronically troubled
computer chip unit, to Seattle Silicon Corp. Terms weren't
disclosed.
   Control Data, which wrote off losses on the operation last
year, said it will continue to buy certain integrated
circuits from VTC.
