                          1990            1989
                      in      per      in      per     %
                   millions  share  millions  share   chg.
                                                                                                       

   Rohm &amp; Haas .....  $54.1   $.81   $53.1     $.80   + 2
   Quantum .........    5.8    .23    75.3     3.00a  -92
